acist and homphobic. Trump playing down covid because it was mainly affecting blue areas came out of the Reagan playbook when AIDS first showed up. Reagan didn't back down on his disregard for lives that weren't cis-het and white. Even when closeted friends were afraid for their lives and asked him to do something. Rest in hell pig.

Most viral edit: Happy Pride month!
